msgstr ""
"انقر فوق :icon:`fa-arrow-right` :guilabel:`إعداد مواقع الاستلام` لـ "
":doc:`إعداد طريقة التوصيل </applications/inventory_and_mrp/inventory/"
"shipping_receiving/setup_configuration/new_delivery_method>`، إذا لزم الأمر، "
"وتأكد من تعيين حقل :guilabel:`المزود` على :guilabel:`الاستلام من المتجر`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/ecommerce/shipping.rst:99
msgid ""
"In the :guilabel:`Stores` tab, click :guilabel:`Add a line` and select the "
"warehouse(s) where customers can collect their orders."
msgstr ""
