#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/structure/pages.rst:61
msgid "Click :guilabel:`Create`."
msgstr "انقر فوق :guilabel:`إنشاء`."

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:61
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:102
msgid ""
"The generated keys are then displayed. Leave the page open for convenience, "
"as copying the keys in Odoo is required next."
msgstr ""
"يتم بعد ذلك عرض المفاتيح المُنشأة. اترك الصفحة مفتوحة للراحة، حيث أن نسخ "
