#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:65
#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:106
msgid "On Odoo"
msgstr "في Odoo"

#: ../../content/applications/websites/website/configuration/spam_protection.rst:67
msgid ""
"From the database dashboard, open the **Settings** app. "
"Under :guilabel:`Integrations`, enable :guilabel:`Cloudflare Turnstile`, "
"then click :guilabel:`Save`."
msgstr ""
"من لوحة بيانات قاعدة البيانات، افتح تطبيق **الإعدادات**. ضمن "
